ada" >USA-Canada</a><ul><li class="item-1035 deeper parent"><a href="/our-work/regions/usa-canada/address-serious-threats" >Address Serious Threats</a><ul><li class="item-1151"><a href="/our-work/regions/usa-canada/address-serious-threats/water-scarcity" >Water Scarcity</a></li><li class="item-1153 deeper parent"><a href="/our-work/regions/usa-canada/address-serious-threats/wns-intro" >White-nose Syndrome</a><ul><li class="item-1258"><a href="/our-work/regions/usa-canada/address-serious-threats/wns-intro/wns-research-grants" >WNS Research Grants</a></li></ul></li><li class="item-1155 deeper parent"><a href="/our-work/regions/usa-canada/address-serious-threats/wind-energy" >Wind Energy</a><ul><li class="item-1265"><a href="/our-work/regions/usa-canada/address-serious-threats/wind-energy/wind-and-wildlife-workshop" >Wind and Wildlife Workshop</a></li></ul></li><li class="item-760"><a href="/our-work/regions/usa-canada/address-serious-threats/cave-mine-destruction-landing" >Cave &amp; Mine Destruction</a></li></ul></li><li class="item-1078"><a href="/our-work/regions/usa-canada/prevent-extinctions" >Prevent Extinctions</a></li><li class="item-1081 deeper parent"><a href="/our-work/regions/usa-canada/protect-mega-populations" >Protect Mega-Populations</a><ul><li class="item-813 deeper parent"><a href="/our-work/regions/usa-canada/protect-mega-populations/bracken-cave" >Bracken Cave</a><ul><li class="item-1034"><a href="/our-work/regions/usa-canada/protect-mega-populations/bracken-cave/member-special-nights" >Member &amp; Special Nights</a></li><li class="item-1037"><a href="/our-work/regions/usa-canada/protect-mega-populations/bracken-cave/public-nights" >Public Nights</a></li><li class="item-1071"><a href="/our-work/regions/usa-canada/protect-mega-populations/bracken-cave/weather-doppler-radar" >Weather &amp; Emergence Times</a></li><li class="item-1074"><a href="/our-work/regions/usa-canada/protect-mega-populations/bracken-cave/bracken-webcam" >Bracken Webcam!</a></li